{"tid":1004577,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[冷戰2.0] 美退出中導條約　俄擴大部署新巡航導彈","createTime":"2019-02-01T14:07:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-01T15:28:18.000Z","uid":51620,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"24a4fd8118a58e9b00049ca95bd19743e9cdda14","tid":1004577,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:07:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/bkn-20190201140522452-0201_00972_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Famenews%2F20190201%2Fbkn-20190201140522452-0201_00972_001.html&d=onMv7Z%2BNYg7J2un5CxWxshX1SmvCJyfLMOcbfj5ioUM%3D&h=52dd9aec\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/amenews/20190201/bkn-20190201140522452-0201_00972_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國國務卿蓬佩奧周五（1日）宣布，美方周六（2日）展開退出《中程導彈條約》的程序。美媒引述消息指，俄羅斯擴大部署被指違約的9M729型陸基巡航導彈，估計現時數量近100枚。專家擔心一旦美國退出該核裁軍條約，勢與俄羅斯觸發軍備競賽，重回冷戰時代。<br />\n<br />\n《中程導彈條約》禁止美俄擁有射程500至5500公里的陸基巡航導彈，華府指俄羅斯9M729的射程超出上限，俄方稱它最大射程為480公里。西方官員透露，俄羅斯去年12月只有3個9M729導彈營，部署西部與中部，但最新情報指導彈營增至4個，地點包括南部及東部。<br />\n<br />\n北約發言人表示，由於無迹象顯示俄羅斯於美國提出的60日限期內、即周六前重新遵守條約，所以必須準備迎接沒有該條約的世界。部分歐洲國家爭論在這情況下，應否讓美方在當地部署相應的導彈抗衡。華府官員亦不滿中國並非條約簽署國，從而在亞洲取得導彈優勢。<br />\n<br />\n卡內基國際和平基金會核武專家近日發表聲明，指俄羅斯違反條約是很嚴重的問題，但美方在這情況下退出只會適得其反，兩國將展開一場導彈競賽。"},{"pid":"2695bc44e2c1db8f72f0d9a64b541ed06199de25","tid":1004577,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯由始至終都冇守過條條約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c30f44005b2ceaf75dbca645b8f750aeb15fc42","tid":1004577,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2695bc44e2c1db8f72f0d9a64b541ed06199de25","tid":1004577,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯由始至終都冇守過條條約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有條約嘅時候整多D 冇左整更多放曬係遠東"},{"pid":"1397580bc63596be826153a4a27ae384a0b528fb","tid":1004577,"uid":121146,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"6c30f44005b2ceaf75dbca645b8f750aeb15fc42","tid":1004577,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2695bc44e2c1db8f72f0d9a64b541ed06199de25","tid":1004577,"uid":121146,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:09:57.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯由始至終都冇守過條條約 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:12:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有條約嘅時候整多D 冇左整更多放曬係遠東"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:14:29.000Z","msg":"卡內基國際和平基金會核武專家近日發表聲明，指俄羅斯違反條約是很嚴重的問題，但美方在這情況下退出只會適得其反，兩國將展開一場導彈競賽。<br />\n<br />\nd所謂專家都痴痴地線 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n美國係聖人？全世界冇人守  唯獨佢要守？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e98c9673880f6c26e2f06c9a5862a4f22d5868","tid":1004577,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:16:13.000Z","msg":"唔退出個陣 俄唔會擴大部署<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4fbb17dd6c818f60c4fb9784551ebeb739dcfa1","tid":1004577,"uid":191352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:16:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b35532db5b7b6caf775b96f1dce66709b852ea6a","tid":1004577,"uid":50386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-01T14:19:13.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯唔守<br />\n支那直頭唔駛守<br />\n搵鳩美國笨柒<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"495bbf43c8425a2a9dbaa941fd95a5549a7b1db6","tid":1004577,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c1e98c9673880f6c26e2f06c9a5862a4f22d5868","tid":1004577,"uid":10757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime